data.title: ZEUS-MP/2: Computational Fluid Dynamics Code
data.name: ZEUS-MP_2
data.description: This repository is the home of the ZEUS-MP 2.0 code, which was created by John Hayes and others at the Laboratory for Computational Astrophysics at UIUC and UCSD.

evidence: "This repository contains the web page and source code for ZEUS-MP 2."

"This repository is being maintained by Brian O'Shea ... as a service to the community, since the server hosting the original ZEUS-MP 2 website is defunct and the code is not being actively developed."
"A second subdirectory, `released_vers`, contains gzipped tar files corresponding to numbered versions of the code, which contain bug fixes and some new features"
